moji.com/images/emoji/apple/ios-11/256/crayon.png\">\n  <h1>@jimp/png</h1>\n  <p>Default Jimp png encoder/decoder.</p>\n</div>\n\n## Available Methods\n\n### Jimp.deflateLevel\n\nSets the deflate level used when saving as PNG format (default is 9)\n\n### Jimp.deflateStrategy\n\nSets the deflate strategy used when saving as PNG format (default is 3)\n\n### Jimp.filterType\n\nSets the filter type used when saving as PNG format (default is automatic filters)\n\n### Jimp.colorType\n\nSets the color type used when saving as PNG format (one of 0, 2, 4, 6)\n\n### Filter Types\n\n```js\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_AUTO;\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_NONE;\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_SUB;\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_UP;\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_AVERAGE;\nJimp.PNG_FILTER_PATH;\n```\n","repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/jimp-dev/jimp.git"},"_source_registry_name":"default","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/jimp-dev/jimp/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/jimp-dev/jimp#readme"}